&lt;p&gt;I am a postdoctoral fellow at &lt;a href=&#34;https://cemse.kaust.edu.sa&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;KAUST&lt;/a&gt; in the group supervised by &lt;a href=&#34;https://richtarik.org&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Prof. Peter Richtárik&lt;/a&gt;. Previously I worked with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kaust.edu.sa/en/study/faculty/diogo-gomes&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Prof. Diogo Gomes&lt;/a&gt; on Computer Algebra for Differential Equations.
I did my PhD in Mathematics at &lt;a href=&#34;http://ysu.am/main/en&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Yerevan State University, Armenia&lt;/a&gt; under the supervision of &lt;a href=&#34;http://math.sci.am/user/grigori-karagulyan&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Prof Grigori Karagulyan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;in-particular-on-automation-of-symbolic-pde-analysis-with-wolfram-mathematica&#34;&gt;In particular, on automation of symbolic PDE analysis with Wolfram Mathematica.&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;i-am-also-collaborating-with-prof-peter-richtárik-https-richtarik-org-on-big-data-optimization-in-machine-learning&#34;&gt;I am also collaborating with &lt;a href=&#34;https://richtarik.org&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Prof. Peter Richtárik&lt;/a&gt; on Big Data Optimization in Machine Learning.&lt;/h1&gt;
</description>
